data.description: Nestled in the coveted Trinity Oaks neighborhood, this impressive 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home is a true gem! Upon entering, you'll be struck by the open floor plan, which seamlessly integrates natural light throughout the home. The living room is a cozy retreat, complete with a charming fireplace. The kitchen is a chef's dream, abundant countertop space, and a convenient breakfast bar for quick bites or casual conversations. The generously sized formal dining room is perfect for hosting elegant gatherings, illuminated by a captivating chandelier! The primary bedroom, thoughtfully located on the first floor, offers a serene escape with its high ceilings, ample natural light, and a well-appointed ensuite bathroom. Dual closets provide organization and convenience, while the ensuite bathroom exudes luxury with dual sinks, a deep soaking tub, and a separate shower, creating a personal oasis! Ascending the stairs, you'll discover a spacious game room, ideal for family entertainment, along with four other spacious bedrooms that are perfect for guests or family members. This home features an office/study room that provides a quiet retreat for work or study. The backyard is a haven of tranquility, boasting a large deck for outdoor dining and relaxation, as well as a spacious yard perfect for outdoor activities and gardening. This home is zoned into the prestigious Comal ISD and provides easy access to 281! Welcome home!
